title: Israel's youth overwhelmingly more right-wing politically than older generations: Poll
description: New polling data show Israel's youth population is overwhelmingly right-leaning politically, in a stark difference from previous generations and Western countries.

title: ‘Anti-Woke’ candidate announces presidential bid
description: (The Center Square) – A new Republican candidate threw his hat into the presidential race late Tuesday, focusing his campaign on an “anti-woke” agenda.
